#: paragraph:45,sentence:208
msgctxt "Paragraph 45: Since he had been drawn to New York for some years, Bill thought the next obvious step was actually to apply for work there, which he did at the New York Unemployment Service Psychological Placement B..."
msgid "Since he had been drawn to New York for some years, Bill thought the next obvious step was actually to apply for work there, which he did at the New York Unemployment Service Psychological Placement Bureau."
