msgstr ""

#: paragraph:47,sentence:225
msgctxt "Paragraph 47: Regarding his time there, Bill wrote of his “lunch time” experiences with the famous and driven Dr. Wolff: At first I thought he really meant for us to have lunch, but that was ridiculous. I could nev..."
msgid "When he wanted something he would say, “I’m leaving in a few minutes; would you please prepare an abstract for the International Biological Psychiatry Congress"
msgstr ""

#: paragraph:47,sentence:226
msgctxt "Paragraph 47: Regarding his time there, Bill wrote of his “lunch time” experiences with the famous and driven Dr. Wolff: At first I thought he really meant for us to have lunch, but that was ridiculous. I could nev..."
msgid "I’ll have to have it in fifteen minutes.” I would go to my typewriter and dash off what he wanted"
msgstr ""

#: paragraph:47,sentence:227
msgctxt "Paragraph 47: Regarding his time there, Bill wrote of his “lunch time” experiences with the famous and driven Dr. Wolff: At first I thought he really meant for us to have lunch, but that was ridiculous. I could nev..."
