msgstr ""

#: paragraph:50,sentence:239
msgctxt "Paragraph 50: This assignment, initiated indirectly from the CIA, both frightened and fascinated thirty-two-year-old Bill—a real, live, James Bond-type secret mission where he knew only as much as was provided at a..."
